The Beijing 2022 Winter Olympic torch relay kicked off on Wednesday in the Chinese capital. The relay will continue until Friday in the three competition zones across central Beijing, Yanqing District and Zhangjiakou in neighboring Hebei Province. The Games will run from February 4 to 20. CGTN reporter Chen Bo covered the torch relay launch in downtown Beijing's Olympic Forest Park in the morning. CGTN reporter Qu Bo covered the torch relay in Beijing's Shougang Park in the afternoon. (Courtesy of International Olympic Committee)